[
    {
        "source_sentence": "大毘盧遮那成佛神變加持經卷",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024a23_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "第四",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024a24_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大唐天竺三藏善無畏",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024a26_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "共沙門一行譯9 密印品密印品第九爾時薄伽梵毘盧遮那觀察諸大眾會，告執金剛祕密主言：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024b01_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「祕密主！",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024b01_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有同如來莊嚴具、同法界趣幖幟，菩薩由是嚴身故，處生死中巡歷諸趣，於一切如來大會以此大菩提幢而幖幟之，諸天、龍、夜叉、乾達婆、阿蘇囉、揭嚕茶、緊那囉、摩睺羅伽、人非人等敬而遶之受教而行。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024b06_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝今諦聽，極善思念，吾當演說。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024b06_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」如是說已，金剛手白言：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024b07_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024b07_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今正是時。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024b07_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024b07_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今正是時。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024b08_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時薄伽梵即便住於身無害力三昧。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024b09_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "住斯定故，說一切如來入三昧耶遍一切無能障礙力無等三昧力明妃曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024b11_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　阿三迷二　呾履二合三迷三　三麼曳四　莎訶五「祕密主！",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024b14_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是明妃示現一切如來地，不越三法道界圓滿地波羅蜜。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024b15_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是密印相，當用定慧手作空心合掌，以定慧二虛空輪並合而建立之。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024b17_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "頌曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024b17_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『此一切諸佛，　　救世之大印，",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024b18_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "正覺三昧耶，　　於此印而住。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024b19_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』「又以定慧手為拳，虛空輪入於掌中，而舒風輪，是為淨法界印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024b21_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024b21_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃陀喃一　達摩馱睹二　薩嚩二合婆嚩句痕三』「復以定慧手，五輪皆等，迭翻相鉤，二虛空輪，首俱相向。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024b25_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "頌曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024b25_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『是名為勝願，　　吉祥法輪印，",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024b26_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世依救世者，　　悉皆轉此輪。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024b27_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』「真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024b28_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　伐折囉引二合呾麼二合句痕二』「復舒定慧二手作歸命合掌，風輪相捻，以二空輪加於上，形如朅伽。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024c02_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "頌曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024c02_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『此大慧刀印，　　一切佛所說，",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024c03_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "能斷於諸見，　　謂俱生身見。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024c04_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』「真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024c05_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　摩訶朅伽微囉闍二　達麼珊捺囉奢二合迦娑訶闍三　薩迦耶捺㗚二合瑟致上二合掣叱曳反諾入迦四　怛他引蘖多引地目訖底丁以反二合儞入社多五　微囉引伽達摩儞入社多𤙖六』「復以定慧二手作虛心合掌，屈二風輪，以二空輪絞之，形如商佉。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024c11_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "頌曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024c11_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『此名為勝願，　　吉祥法螺印，",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024c12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸佛世之師，　　菩薩救世者，",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024c13_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "皆說無垢法，　　至寂靜涅槃。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024c14_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』「真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024c15_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　暗』「復以定慧手相合普舒散之，猶如健吒，二地輪二空輪相持，令火風輪和合。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024c17_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "頌曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024c17_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『吉祥願蓮華，　　諸佛救世者，",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024c18_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不壞金剛座，　　覺悟名為佛，",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024c19_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩提與佛子，　　悉皆從是生。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024c20_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』「真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024c21_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　阿去急呼』「復以定慧手，五輪外向為拳，建立火輪。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024c22_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舒二風輪屈為鉤形，在傍持之。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024c23_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "虛空地輪並而直上，水輪交合如拔折囉。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024c24_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "頌曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024c24_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『金剛大慧印，　　能壞無智城，",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024c25_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "曉寤睡眠者，　　天人不能壞。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024c26_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』「真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024c27_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多伐折羅二合𧹞一　𤙖』「復以定慧手，五輪內向為拳，建立火輪。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024c28_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以二風輪置傍，屈二虛空相並。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024c29_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "頌曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0024c29_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『此印摩訶印，　　所謂如來頂，",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025a01_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "適纔結作之，　　即同於世尊。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025a02_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』「真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025a03_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　𤙖𤙖』「復以智慧手為拳，置於眉間。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025a04_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "頌曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025a04_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『此名毫相藏，　　佛常滿願印，",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025a05_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以纔作此故，　　即同仁中勝。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025a06_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』「真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025a07_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　阿去急呼痕若急呼』「住瑜伽座，持鉢相應，以定慧手俱在臍間，是名釋迦牟尼大鉢印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025a10_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025a11_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　婆上急呼』「復次以智慧手，上向而作施無畏形。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025a12_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "頌曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025a12_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『能施與一切，　　眾生類無畏，",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025a13_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若結此大印，　　名施無畏者。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025a14_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』「真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025a15_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　薩婆他二　爾娜爾娜三　佩也那奢娜四　莎訶五』「復次以智慧手，下垂作施願形。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025a17_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "頌曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025a17_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『如是與願印，　　世依之所說，",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025a18_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "適纔結此者，　　諸佛滿其願。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025a19_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』「真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025a20_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　嚩囉娜伐折囉二合引怛麼二合迦二　莎訶』「復以智慧手為拳，而舒風輪，以毘俱胝形住於等引。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025a23_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "頌曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025a23_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『以如是大印，　　諸佛救世尊，",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025a24_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "恐怖諸障者，　　隨意成悉地。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025a25_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由結是印故，　　大惡魔軍眾，",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025a26_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "及餘諸障者，　　馳散無所礙。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025a27_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』「真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025a28_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　麼訶引沫羅嚩底丁以反二　捺奢嚩路嗢婆二合吠平三　摩訶引昧怛𭌆也三合毘庾二合嗢蘗二合底丁以反四　莎訶』「復次以智慧手為拳，而舒火輪水輪，以虛空輪而在其下。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025b04_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "頌曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025b04_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『此名一切佛，　　世依悲生眼，",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025b05_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "想置於眼界，　　智者成佛眼。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025b06_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』「真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025b07_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　伽伽那嚩囉洛吃灑二合儜上二　迦嚕儜麼那三　怛他引蘗多斫吃芻二合四　莎訶』「復次以定摩手，五輪內向為拳，而舒風輪，圓屈相合。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025b11_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "頌曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025b11_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『此勝願索印，　　壞諸造惡者，",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025b12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "真言者結之，　　能縛諸不善。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025b13_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』「真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025b14_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　係係摩訶引播奢二　鉢羅二合娑嘮那𭌆也二合三　薩埵馱睹四　微模訶迦五　怛他引蘖多引地目吃底丁以反二合儞入社多六　莎訶七』「復次以定慧手一合為拳，舒智慧手，風輪屈第三節，猶如環相。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025b19_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "頌曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025b19_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『如是名鉤印，　　諸佛救世者，",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025b20_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "招集於一切，　　住於十地位，",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025b21_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩提大心者，　　及惡思眾生。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025b22_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』「真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025b23_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　阿去急呼薩婆怛囉引二合鉢囉二合底丁以反訶諦二　怛他引蘖黨矩奢三　菩提浙𭌆耶二合鉢𭌆布邏迦四　莎訶五』「即此鉤印，舒其火輪而少屈之，是謂如來心印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025b28_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025b28_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　壤怒嗢婆二合嚩二　莎訶三』「復以此印舒其水輪而竪立之，名如來臍印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025c02_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025c03_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　阿沒㗚二合覩嗢婆二合嚩二　莎訶』「即以此印直舒水輪，餘亦竪之，名如來腰印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025c06_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025c07_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　怛他引蘗多三婆嚩二　莎訶』「復以定慧手作空心合掌，以二風輪屈入於內，二水輪亦然，其二地輪令少屈，而伸火輪，此是如來藏印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025c12_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025c12_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼薩婆怛他引蘗帝弊毘也反一　㘕㘕𡀩𡀩二　莎嚩二合訶』「即以此印散其水輪向上置之，名大界印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025c15_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025c16_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　麗魯補𭌆微矩麗二　莎訶三』「即以此印，其二火輪鉤屈相合，散舒風輪，名無堪忍大護印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025c20_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0025c20_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼薩婆怛他引蘗帝弊毘也反，下同一　薩婆佩也微蘗帝弊二　微濕嚩目契弊三　薩婆他引四　唅欠五　囉訖灑二合摩訶引沫麗六　薩婆怛他引蘗多本抳也二合儜入社帝七　𤙖𤙖八　怛囉引二合吒輕怛囉吒同上九　阿鉢囉二合底丁以反訶諦十　莎訶十一』「復以風輪而散舒之，空輪並入其中，名普光印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0026a03_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0026a03_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　入嚩引二合囉引摩履儞平二　怛他引蘗多㗚旨二合三　莎訶四』「又以定慧手作空心合掌，以二風輪持火輪側，名如來甲印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0026a07_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「屈二水輪，二空輪合入掌中押二水輪甲上，是如來舌相印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0026a09_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0026a09_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　怛他引蘗多爾訶嚩二合二　薩底也二　合達摩鉢囉二合瑟恥二合多三　莎訶四』「以此印，令風水輪屈而相捻，空輪向上而少屈之，火輪正直相合，地輪亦如是，名如來語門印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0026a15_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0026a15_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　怛他引蘗多摩訶引嚩無各反吃怛囉三合二　微濕嚩二合壤引曩摩護娜也三　莎訶四』「如前印，以二風輪屈入掌中向上，名如來牙印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0026a20_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0026a20_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　怛他引蘗多能去瑟吒羅三合二　囉娑囉娑引釳囉二合三　參鉢囉引二合博迦四　薩婆怛他引蘗多五　微灑也參婆上嚩六　莎訶七』「又如前印相，以二風輪向上置之，屈第三節，名如來辯說印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0026a26_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0026a26_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　阿振底也二合娜部二合多二　𡀔波嚩引三摩哆上鉢囉引二合鉢多二合三　微輸上馱娑嚩二合囉四　莎訶』「復次以定慧手和合一相作空心合掌，二地輪空輪屈入相合，此是如來持十力印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0026b02_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0026b03_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　捺奢麼浪伽輕達囉二　𤙖參髯三　莎訶四』「又如前印，以二空輪風輪屈上節相合，是如來念處印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0026b07_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0026b07_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　怛他引蘗多娑麼㗚三合底二　薩埵係哆弊毘庾反嗢蘗多三　伽伽那糝忙引糝麼四　莎訶四』「又如前印，以二空輪在水輪上，名一切法平等開悟印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0026b12_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0026b12_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　薩婆達摩三麼哆鉢囉引二合鉢多二合二　怛他引蘗哆弩蘗多三　莎訶四』「復以定慧手合為一，以二風輪加火輪上，餘如前，是普賢如意珠印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0026b17_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0026b17_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　參麼哆弩蘗多二　微囉若達摩儞入社多三　摩訶引摩訶四　莎訶五』「即此虛心合掌，以二風輪屈在二火輪下，餘如前，是慈氏印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0026b22_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0026b22_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　阿爾單若也二　薩婆薩埵引奢夜弩蘗多三　莎訶四』「又如前印，以二虛空輪入中，名虛空藏印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0026b25_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0026b26_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　阿去迦引奢參麼哆弩蘗多二　微質怛㘕二合嚩囉達囉三　莎訶四』「又如前印，以二水輪二地輪屈入掌中，二風輪火輪相合，是除一切蓋障印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0026c01_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0026c01_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　阿去急呼薩埵係哆弊毘庾反嗢蘗多二　怛㘕二　合三　㘕㘕四　莎訶五』「如前以定慧手相合，散舒五輪猶如鈴鐸，以虛空地輪和合相持作蓮華形，是觀自在印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0026c06_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0026c06_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　薩婆怛他引蘗哆嚩路吉多二　羯嚕儜麼也三　囉囉囉𤙖若四　莎訶五』「如前以定慧手作空心合掌，猶如未開敷蓮，是得大勢印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0026c10_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0026c10_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　髯髯娑急呼二　莎訶三』「如前以定慧手，五輪內向為拳，舉二風輪猶如針鋒，二虛空輪加之，是多羅尊印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0026c13_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0026c14_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　哆囇哆𭌆抳二　羯嚕拏嗢婆上二合吠平三　莎訶四』「如前印，舉二風輪參差相押，是毘俱胝印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0026c17_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0026c18_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　薩婆佩也怛囉引二合散儞入二　𤙖娑破二合吒也三　莎訶四』「如前，以定慧手空心合掌，水輪空輪皆入於中，是白處尊印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0026c22_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0026c22_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　怛他引蘗多微灑也三婆上吠平二　鉢曇摩二合忙𭌆儞入三　莎訶四』「如前印，屈二風輪置虛空輪下，相去猶如穬麥，是何耶揭哩嚩印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027a04_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027a04_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　佉娜也畔若娑破二合吒也二　莎訶三』「同前印，申二水輪風輪，餘如拳，是地藏菩薩印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027a08_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027a08_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　訶訶訶二　蘇上怛弩三　莎訶四』「復以定慧手作空中合掌，火輪水輪交結相持，以二風輪置二虛空輪上猶如鉤形，餘如前，是聖者文殊師利印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027a13_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027a13_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　係係矩忙囉二　微目吃底二合鉢他悉體他以反二合多三　娑麼二合囉娑麼二合囉四　鉢囉二合底然五　莎訶六』「以三昧手為拳，而舉風輪猶如鉤形，是光網鉤印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027a18_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027a18_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　係係矩忙引囉二　忙引耶蘗多娑嚩二合婆去嚩悉體他以反二合多三　莎訶四』「即如前印，一切輪相皆少屈之，是無垢光印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027a22_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027a23_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　係矩忙引囉二　微質怛囉二合蘗底矩忙引囉三　麼弩娑麼二合囉四　莎訶五』「如前，以智慧手為拳，其風火輪相合為一舒之，是繼室尼刀印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027a28_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027a28_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　係係矩忙引𭌆計二　娜耶壤難娑摩二合囉三　鉢囉二合底然四　莎訶五』「如前，以智慧手為拳，而申火輪猶如戟形，是優波髻室尼戟印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027b04_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027b04_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　頻去娜夜壤難二　係矩忙引𭌆計三　莎訶四』「如前，以三昧手為拳，而舒水輪地輪，是地慧幢印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027b08_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027b08_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　係娑麼二合囉壤那計覩二　莎訶三』「以慧手為拳，而舒風輪猶如鉤形，是請召童子印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027b12_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027b12_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　阿去羯囉灑二合也薩鑁引二　矩嚕阿去然三　矩忙引囉寫四　莎訶五』「如前以定慧手為拳，舒二風輪屈節相合，是諸奉教者印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027b16_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027b16_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　阿去急呼微娑麼二合也儜曳平二　莎訶三』「如前，以定慧手為拳而舒火輪，屈第三節，是除疑怪金剛印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027b20_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027b20_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　微麼底掣鵄曳反諾迦二　莎訶三』「舉毘鉢舍那臂，作施無畏手，是施無畏者印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027b23_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027b24_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　阿佩延娜娜二　莎訶三』「如前，舒智手而上舉之，是除惡趣印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027b27_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027b28_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　阿弊毘庾反達囉儜上薩埵馱敦二　莎訶三』「如前，以慧手掩心，是救護慧印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027c02_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027c02_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　係摩訶引摩訶二　娑麼二合囉鉢囉二合底然三　莎訶四』「如前，以慧手作持華狀，是大慈生印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027c05_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027c06_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　娑嚩二合制妬嗢蘗二合多二　莎訶三』「如前，以慧手覆心，稍屈火輪，是悲念者印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027c09_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027c10_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　羯嚕儜沒麗二合眤多二　莎訶三』「如前，以慧手作施願相，是除一切熱惱印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027c13_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027c14_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　係嚩囉娜二　嚩囉鉢囉二合引鉢多二合三　莎訶四』「如前，以智慧手如執持真多摩尼寶形，是不思議慧印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027c18_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027c18_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　薩摩舍鉢𭌆布囉二　莎訶三』「如前，以定慧手為拳，令二火輪開敷，是地藏旗印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027c22_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027c22_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　訶訶訶微娑麼二合曳平二　莎訶三』「慧手為拳而舒三輪，是寶處印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027c25_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027c25_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　係摩訶引摩訶二　莎訶三』「以此慧手舒其水輪，是寶手菩薩印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027c28_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0027c29_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　囉怛怒二合嗢婆上嚩二　莎訶三』「以定慧手作返相叉合掌，定手空輪、慧手地輪相交，般若於三昧亦復如是，餘如跋折羅狀，是持地印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028a05_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028a05_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　達囉尼尼仁反達囉二　莎訶三』「如前，作五股金剛戟形，是寶印手印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028a08_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028a09_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　囉怛娜二合儞入喇爾二合多二　莎訶三』「即以此印令一切輪相合，是發堅固意印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028a12_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028a13_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　伐折囉二合三婆嚩二　莎訶三』「如前，以定慧二手作刀，是虛空無垢菩薩印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028a16_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028a17_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　伽伽娜引難多愚者囉莎訶』「如前，輪印，是虛空慧印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028a20_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028a20_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　斫吃囉二合嚩入喇底丁以反二合二　莎訶三』「如前，商佉印，是清淨慧印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028a23_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028a23_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　達磨三婆嚩二　莎訶三』「如前，蓮華印，是行慧印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028a26_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028a26_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　鉢曇摩二合囉上耶二　莎訶三』「同前，青蓮華印而稍開敷，是安住慧印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028a29_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028a30_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　壤弩嗢婆二合嚩二　莎訶三』「如前，以二手相合，而屈水輪相交入於掌中，二火輪地輪向上相持，而舒風輪屈第三節令不相著猶如穬麥，是執金剛印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028b05_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028b05_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多伐折囉𧹞一　戰拏摩訶引𡀔灑拏𤙖二』「如前印，以二空輪地輪屈入掌中，是忙莽雞印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028b09_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028b09_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多伐折囉𧹞一　怛㗚二合吒輕怛㗚吒同上二　若衍底丁以反莎訶二』「如前，以定慧手諸輪返叉，相糺向於自體而旋轉之，般若空輪加三昧虛輪，是金剛鎖印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028b14_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028b14_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多伐折囉𧹞一　𤙖滿馱滿馱二　慕吒耶慕吒耶三　伐折𡀔嗢婆二合吠平四　薩婆怛囉引二合鉢囉二合底丁以反訶帝五　莎訶六』「以此金剛鎖印，少屈虛空輪以持風輪而不相至，是忿怒月黶印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028b19_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028b19_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多伐折囉二合𧹞一　曷唎二合急呼𤙖發吒輕二　莎訶三』「如前，以定慧手為拳，建立二風輪而以相持，是金剛針印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028b23_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028b23_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多伐折囉二合𧹞一　薩婆達磨儞入吠達儞二　伐折囉引二合素旨嚩囉泥三　莎訶四』「如前，以定慧手為拳而置於心，是金剛拳印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028b28_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028b28_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多伐折囉二合𧹞一　薩破二合吒也伐折囉二合三婆吠平二　莎訶三』「以三昧手為拳，舉翼開敷，智慧手亦作拳，而舒風輪如忿怒相擬形，是無能勝印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028c02_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028c03_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多伐折囉二合𧹞一　訥達𭌆沙二合摩訶引嚧灑拏二　佉引捺耶薩鑁引怛他引蘗單然矩嚕三　莎訶四』「以定慧手為拳，作相擊勢持之，是阿毘目佉印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028c08_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028c08_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多伐折囉二合𧹞一　係阿毘目佉摩訶鉢囉二合戰拏二　佉引娜也緊旨囉引也徙三　三麼耶麼弩薩麼囉二合囉四　莎訶五』「如前，持鉢相，是釋迦鉢印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028c12_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028c12_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　薩嚩訖麗二合奢儞入素捺耶二　薩婆達摩嚩始多引鉢囉二合鉢多三　伽伽那三迷四　莎訶五』「釋迦毫相印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028c16_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如上，又以慧手指峯聚置頂上，是一切佛頂印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028c17_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028c17_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　鑁鑁二　𤙖𤙖𤙖三　發吒輕四　莎訶五』「以三昧手為拳舒火風輪，而以虛空加地水輪上，其智慧手申風火輪入三昧掌中，亦以虛空加地水輪上如在刀鞘，是不動尊印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028c22_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如前，金剛慧印，是降三世印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0028c23_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如前，以定慧手合為一相，其地水輪皆向下，而申火輪二峯相連，屈二風輪置於第三節上，並虛空輪如三目形。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029a02_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是如來頂印佛菩薩母。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029a03_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復以三昧手覆而舒之，慧手為拳而舉風輪猶如蓋形，是白傘佛頂印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029a05_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如前，刀印，是勝佛頂印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029a06_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如前，輪印，是最勝佛頂印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029a07_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如前，鉤印，慧手為拳舉其風輪而少屈之，是除業佛頂印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029a09_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如前，佛頂印，是火聚佛頂印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029a10_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如前，蓮華印，是發生佛頂印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029a11_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如前，商佉印，是無量音聲佛頂印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029a12_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「以智慧手為拳置在眉間，是真多摩尼毫相印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029a14_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如前，佛頂印，是佛眼印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029a15_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復有少異，所謂金剛標相。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029a16_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「智慧手在心，如執蓮華像，直申奢摩他臂，五輪上舒而外向距之，是無能勝印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029a18_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「定慧手向內為拳，二虛空輪上向屈之如口，是無能勝明妃印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029a20_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「以智慧手承頰，是自在天印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029a21_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「即以此印令風火輪差戾申之，是普華天子印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029a23_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「同前印，以虛空輪在於掌中，是光鬘天子印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029a25_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「同前印，以虛空風輪作持華相，是滿意天子印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029a27_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「以智慧手虛空水輪相加，其風火輪地輪皆散舒之以掩其耳，是遍音聲天印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029a29_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「定慧相合，二虛空輪圓屈，其餘四輪亦如是，是名地神印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029b02_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如前，以智慧手作施無畏相，以空輪在於掌中，是請召火天印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029b04_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「即以施無畏形，以虛空輪持水輪第二節，是一切諸仙印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029b06_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "隨其次第，相應用之。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029b06_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如前以定慧手相合，風輪地輪入於掌中，餘皆上向，是焰摩但茶印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029b08_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「慧手向下猶如健吒，是焰摩妃鐸印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029b09_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「以三昧手為拳，舒風火輪，是暗夜天印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029b10_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「即以此印又屈風輪，是嚕達羅戟印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029b11_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如前印，作持蓮華形，是梵天明妃印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029b12_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如前印，屈其風輪加火輪背第三節，是嬌末離爍底印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029b14_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「即以此印，令風輪加虛空上，是那羅延后輪印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029b16_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「三昧手為拳，令虛空輪直上，是焰魔七母鎚印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029b18_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「仰其定手如持劫鉢羅相，是遮文茶印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029b19_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如前，朅伽印，是涅哩底刀印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029b20_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如前，輪印，以三昧手為之，是那羅延輪印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029b21_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「以轉定慧手左右相加，是難徒拔難陀二雲印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029b23_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如前，申三昧手，虛空地輪相加，是商羯羅三戟印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029b25_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如前，伸三昧手，虛空地輪相持，是商羯羅后印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029b27_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「即以此印直舒三輪，是商羯羅妃印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029b28_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「以三昧手作蓮華相，是梵天印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029b29_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「因作潔白觀，是月天印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029c01_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「以定慧手顯現合掌，屈虛空輪置水輪側，是日天輿輅印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029c03_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「合般若三昧手，地輪風輪內向，其水火輪相持如弓，是社耶毘社耶印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029c05_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如前，幢印，是風天印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029c06_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「仰三昧手在於臍輪，智慧手空風相持，向身運動如奏音樂，是妙音天費拏印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029c08_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如前，羂索印，是諸龍印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029c09_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如前，妙音天印，而屈風輪交空輪上，是一切阿脩羅印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029c11_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029c11_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　蘖囉邏延二　莎訶三』「內向為拳而舒水輪，是乾闥婆印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029c13_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029c13_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　微輸馱薩嚩二合囉嚩引係儞平二　莎訶三』「即以此印而屈風輪，是一切藥叉印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029c16_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029c17_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　藥乞釵二合濕嚩二合囉二合莎訶三』「又以此印，虛空輪地輪相持而申火風，是藥叉女印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029c21_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029c21_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　藥乞叉二合尾儞耶二合達𭌆二　莎訶三』「內向為拳而舒火輪，是諸毘舍遮印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029c24_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029c25_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　比舍引遮蘖底丁以反二　莎訶三』「改屈火輪，是諸毘舍支印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029c28_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0029c28_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　比旨比旨二　莎訶三』「如前，以定慧手相合，並虛空輪而建立之，是一切執曜印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0030a02_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0030a02_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　蘖囉二合醯濕靺二合𭌆耶二合鉢囉引二合鉢多二合二　孺底丁以反麼耶三　莎訶四』「復以此印，虛空火輪相交，是一切宿印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0030a06_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0030a07_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　娜吃灑二合怛囉二合二　儞入囊捺儞平曳三　莎訶四』「即以此印，屈二水輪入於掌中，是諸羅剎娑印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0030a11_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0030a11_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　囉引吃灑二合娑引地鉢多曳二　莎訶三』「申三昧手以覆面門，爾賀嚩觸之，是諸荼吉尼印。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0030a15_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "真言曰：",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0030a15_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南麼三曼多勃馱喃一　頡𭌆二合莎訶急呼二』「祕密主！",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0030a17_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是上首諸如來印，從如來信解生，即同菩薩之幖幟，其數無量。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0030a18_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又祕密主！",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0030a18_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "乃至身分舉動住止，應知皆是密印；",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0030a19_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舌相所轉眾多言說，應知皆是真言。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0030a20_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故祕密主！",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0030a20_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "真言門修菩薩行諸菩薩已發菩提心，應當住如來地，畫漫荼羅。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0030a22_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若異此者，同謗諸佛菩薩，越三昧耶，決定墮於惡趣。",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0030a23_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」大毘盧遮那成佛神變加持經卷第四",
        "from": "T18n0848_004:0030a24_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]